<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg"></div>
  <div class="cta-particles">
    <div class="particle p1"></div>
    <div class="particle p2"></div>
    <div class="particle p3"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Tienes un proyecto en mente?</h2>
      <p>
        Agenda una llamada gratuita de 30 minutos. Analizamos tu caso,
        te propongo soluciones y te doy un presupuesto sin compromiso.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/#contacto" class="btn btn-white">Empecemos a trabajar &rarr;</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/darwinva97" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline">Ver mi GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4, #7c3aed);
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 40%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-particles {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .particle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .p1 {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    top: -100px;
    right: -50px;
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .p2 {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    bottom: -50px;
    left: 10%;
    animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  .p3 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    top: 30%;
    left: 60%;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite 2s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: #fff;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
</style>
